quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  17,87,"Halali khutsimbabaasi tsirula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Toto obulayi bubwe khwiwe ni obukhongo."
  17,88,"Boola mbu: “Kata nibekhung’asia Abandu nende Amajini mbu kho barere eshifwana shinga Ikurani ino, shibakhanyala okhurera eshifwana ngayo tawe kata nibakhonyana abeene khubeene.”"
  17,89,"Ne toto khwenoosilia Abandu buli amachelasio mu Ikurani ino. Halali Abandu abaanji bakhayanga koosi okhuyiniakho okhukhaya (Nyasaye) butswa."
  17,90,"Ne (abakhayi) baboola mbu, "Shikhunyala okhusuubila tawe okhula okhukhulukusilie isebele mwiloba."
  17,91,"Nohomba obe nende omukunda kwetsitende nende tsizabibu, mana chikhulukusiemo emialo makhulukusia."
  17,92,"Nohomba okhukwisiekhwo likulu ebitonye ebitonye shingala wishemulanga, nohomba okhurerere Nyasaye nende abamalaika obweni khubweni."
  17,93,"Nohomba obe nende inzu yeyidhahabu, nohomba onine mwikulu. Ne shikhulasuubila okhunina khwao tawe okhula okhwishilie eshitabu khusome. Boola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi nomutswenufu. Esie endisa omundu, Omurumwa (shendi Malaika nohomba Nyasaye tawe).”"
  17,94,"Ne shibulaho shiakayila abandu okhusuubila olwa obulunjifu bwabetsela halali baboola mbu: “Koo, Nyasaye yaruma omundu okhuba Omurumwa wuwe?”"
  17,95,"Boola mbu: “Khushialo abamalaika babetsangakho nibachenda nibehotseresiye, toto khwakheshiyie okhurula mwikulu Malaika yaba Omurumwa.”"
  17,96,"Boola mbu: “Nyasaye ayela okhuba omuloli hakari wanje ninanyu. Toto Ye yamanya obulayi Abasumba be, ne abalolanga muno.”"